X: 313
T: Now the Light Has Gone Away
%%combinevoices 1
C: Words: Frances Ridley Havergal, 1869. 
C: Music: 'Müde bin ich, geh zur Ruh' from Liederbuch für Kleinkinder-Schulen, 1842. 
C: Setting: "Common Service Book" (ULCA), 1917, alt.
C: copyright: public domain.  This score is a part of the Open Hymnal Project, 2009 Revision.
M: 4/4 % time signature
L: 1/4 % default length
